Package sample

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • sample.Controller
  • public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    Class specifies the functions that Controller should perform to execute User Commands The Controller class defines the Controller responsibilities in the MVC model, which allows the FXML file to describe the User Interface. The result is a program that keeps business logic and functions separate from the User Interface according to the MVC design pattern.
    Author:
    leefowler
